SECTION 1. The following barrios in the Municipality of Sante Fe, Province of Romblon, are created:

Barrio Magsaysay to be composed of the present sitios of Catolog, Palate, Layog, Simbiray and Mambong;

Barrio Mat-i to be composed of the present sitios of Mat-i, Guinpasilan, Bolagsong, Aglagtang and Isabels;

Barrio Agmanic to be composed of the present sitios of Agmanic, Capdang, Tipolo-Bahol, Bolocawe, Binaloca and Cabali-an;

Barrio Tabugon to be composed of the present sitios of Tabugon, Cabungahan, Pittigo, Guinpoyungan, Grande, Cahawagan and Hinaclopan;

Barrio Canyayo to be composed of the present sitios of Canyayo, Lonoc, Campong, Payong-payong and Capid;

Barrio Pandan to be composed of the present sitios of pandan, Sayao, Guinda, Camonsel, Capinayan, Baybay, Candoyong, Lojo and Catopaz;

Barrio Danao Norte to be composed of the present sitios of Danao Norte, Hacienda, Sabang, Timba-on, Danao Sur and Bunga;

Barrio Pinamihagan to be composed of the present sitios of Pinamihagan, Pacol, Buyahon, Sugod, Pinaman-dayan, Pajo and Añgas; and
